data.description: Awesome home overlooking the golf course,  nestled amongst mature Live Oaks w a porch that spans the entire back, offering amazing views. Inside you will find a wonderfully updated bright open concept floorplan with soaring living room ceilings. The master suite is separated from the other rooms and comes with a large master bath plus a bonus office/studio. The other rooms offer tall ceilings and ample space and access to back porch. Come home to this spacious and peaceful retreat, minutes from the lake.
